{SAILING}
Sailing is a very popular sport in this area.The members of the yacht club meet every weekend.Usually they have races too.Every month there is a special race. The boats range from large yachts with colourful sails and fancy names to small dinghys.
{CLIMBING}
This area is very popular for climbing.Particularly on Ben Nevis which is the highest mountain in Scotland.{ {FOOTBALL} This year Fort William's football club has gained membership in the Highland League, also this year they have made it into the Scottish Cup.
